## \uc0\u55357 \u56960  Quick Start\
\
Create `hello.nvs`:\
```nvs\
func main() \{\
    print("Hello, NaveScript!")\
    \
    // Concurrency example\
    go func() \{\
        print("Running in parallel!")\
    \}()\
    \
    // Channel example\
    ch := make(chan int)\
    go func() \{\
        ch <- 42\
    \}()\
    print(<-ch)\
\}\
```\
